  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Pan Pacific Whistler Mountainside is the perfect combination of slope-side access and a village location. Enjoy slope-watching from the hotel's heated outdoor pool or discover how the Canadian's do après at the on-site Dubh Linn Gate Pub.</p>
<h2>Great slope access</h2>
<p>Located at the base of the slopes you can't miss the Pan Pacific Whistler Mountainside as you ski down into town. Just follow the sound of music and clinking glasses to the hotel's popular Dubh Linn Gate Pub for some of Whistler's best après.</p>
<p>The gondolas to both mountains are right outside. Directly opposite is the Excalibur Gondola with access to Blackcomb Mountain and a short walk from there is Whistler Village Gondola with access to Whistler Mountain.</p>
<h2>Village location</h2>
<p>You have Whistler's huge range of restaurants and bars right on your doorstep. The main Village Stroll is just a few steps away with world class restaurants, cosy cafes, boutique shops and lively bars to explore.</p>
<p>The hotel's Dubh Linn Gate Pub is a hot spot for après, or try out the sister hotel's <a data-udi="umb://document/3bbc43f0ea944610ab741243b3af4933" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3bbc43f0ea944610ab741243b3af4933}" title="Pan Pacific Whistler Village Centre" data-anchor="#">Pan Pacific Whistler Village Centre</a> Raven Room for their popular <span>craft cocktails, local beers, large wine selection and great food menu.</span></p>
<h2><span>All-suite accommodation</span></h2>
<p><span>The Pan Pacific Whistler Mountainside's all-suite room types are the perfect home from home. All rooms have full kitchens so you can self cater or head out to the Village Stroll for some fantastic dining options.</span></p>
<p><span>Cosy up by your fireplace or marvel at the snowy landscape from your balcony with either a mountain or village view.</span></p>
<h2><span>Heated pool with mountain view</span></h2>
<p><span>With access to a heated outdoor pool and two hot tubs on Whistler's most scenic deck, you're guaranteed a relaxing getaway at the Pan Pacific Whistler Mountainside. The wellness area also has a steam room and fitness room as well as a range of beauty and massage treatments which you can book locally.</span></p>]]></description>
